'''內{{zy|眥|zì|ㄗˋ}}{{zy|贅|zhuì|ㄓㄨㄟˋ}}皮'''亦稱'''内眦皱襞''' ({{lang-en|epicanthic fold}})，俗稱'''蒙古褶'''，是人類[[上眼瞼|上眼瞼]]眼框內側的皮膚皺摺，出現於[[東北亞|東北亞]]、[[東亞|東亞]]、[[中亚|中亚]]、[[南亞|南亞]] 和[[美洲|美洲本土]]民族、還有[[北歐|北歐]]和[[東歐|東歐]]人、[[南非|南非]]的[[科伊桑人|科伊桑人]]和[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]原住民等，各人種都有可能出現這個特徵。<ref>Montagu, A. (1989). Growing Young. Bergin & Garvey: CT.</ref><ref name=askd>{{cite web |title=Epicanthus |url=http://epicanthus.askdefine.com/ |accessdate=25 April 2014 |archive-date=2017-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229052202/http://epicanthus.askdefine.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = epicanthic fold (anatomy) |url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/189688/epicanthic-fold |work = Encyclopaedia Britannica |accessdate = 25 April 2014 |archive-date = 2014-11-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101102111/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/189688/epicanthic-fold |dead-url = no }}</ref>

